n according to the actual amount."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"break_option","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p206","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"13.4"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p207","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"Article 14"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p207","offsets":[{"start":11,"text":"Return of this Unit"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p208","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"14.1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p208","offsets":[{"start":79,"text":"Lessee shall return this unit emptied and at the original state in delivery and all keys to Lessor (or the property company) and conduct acceptance together with Lessor (or the property company) on the lease duration date or advance termination date of the Contract or within the period specified by Lessor (if any). Lessor shall make compesenation for damage (excluding natural wear). Lessee shall bear all expenses incurred from direct or indirect damage to other places beyond this unit or the third party in the process of returning this unit and other sites, facilities and equipment dedicated for Lessee to the original state in delivery."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"reinstatement_clause","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18",